Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.99,0:10:49.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蚊香和電蚊香都準備OK
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.01,0:10:52.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我原本以為過一會兒就會消失的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.49,0:10:56.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有消失  深夜的  最上川
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.25,0:11:22.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說一寸的蚊子有五寸的靈魂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.46,0:11:25.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還是放棄好了  乖乖地去睡覺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.09,0:11:27.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你這傢伙吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.14,0:11:36.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨呀！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.24,0:11:51.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做了無謂的殺生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.01,0:11:54.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺死你！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.37,0:12:02.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎麼打  不管怎麼打
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.38,0:12:05.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每年每年都無法絕跡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.43,0:12:07.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都已經不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.69,0:12:09.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事了！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.81,0:12:11.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.80,0:12:14.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡…這個家已經不能住了！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.36,0:12:16.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能搬家了！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.88,0:12:28.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以為現在幾點了啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.11,0:12:30.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我安靜地睡覺！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
