Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.00,0:17:36.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石頭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.81,0:17:37.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剪刀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.90,0:17:39.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.79,0:17:52.89,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(0,600)}一句話時間
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.12,0:18:01.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去檢索的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.61,0:18:03.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都可能會出現
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.22,0:18:12.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  美緒  正找你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.05,0:18:14.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事啊  姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.77,0:18:17.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐正好有點急事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.88,0:18:21.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想讓你代替我去街道會的攤位幫幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.92,0:18:25.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒  這種事讓媽媽去做就好了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.41,0:18:27.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽和朋友去踢藤球了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.34,0:18:31.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且你看  有一萬円的打工費哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.66,0:18:33.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.21,0:18:41.19,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}街道會大福展銷會 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.67,0:18:37.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一萬円的打工費真誘人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.28,0:18:40.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正很閑  就去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.06,0:18:46.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼超可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.42,0:18:47.24,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(600,300)\fad(0,600)}日\N常\N之\N39
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.48,0:18:50.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  被算計了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.34,0:18:52.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟透了  這是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.57,0:18:53.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這到底是什麼鬼東西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.93,0:18:55.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我要陷入這種困境
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.47,0:19:01.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且街道會的活動居然是兩個人在街邊賣大福
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.31,0:19:02.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.74,0:19:04.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好丟臉啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.63,0:19:06.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.42,0:19:07.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太丟臉了啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.11,0:19:10.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路人都用可悲的眼神望著我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.67,0:19:11.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就能招來客人？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.15,0:19:15.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是吉祥物的大福君？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.45,0:19:18.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有眼睛也沒有嘴  只有一張白臉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.08,0:19:22.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這都已經不是大福君了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.28,0:19:23.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是大福啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.83,0:19:25.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.35,0:19:26.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個大福展銷會
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.17,0:19:29.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是什麼展銷會啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.16,0:19:35.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.16,0:19:42.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全出局了呢  這個
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.30,0:19:45.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.12,0:19:46.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看上去好噁心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.44,0:19:49.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接招
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.32,0:19:51.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手  很痛的啦  快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.06,0:19:55.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等等  下面沒有戴護具啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.00,0:19:58.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下面沒有戴護具啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.69,0:20:01.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…你們  給我住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.41,0:20:03.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生氣了  快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.05,0:20:07.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  搞什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.97,0:20:12.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.88,0:20:30.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請不要這樣破壞大福的形象
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.06,0:20:32.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.86,0:20:34.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看我的示範
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.99,0:20:36.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快把這個取下來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.07,0:20:38.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才不想請打工的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.33,0:20:44.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別傻站著  去幫我看攤子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.13,0:20:48.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  為了一萬円的打工費  我就忍了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.03,0:21:00.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糯米粉  小紅豆  和三盆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.03,0:21:00.62,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}和三盆：一種上等砂糖，產於香川縣、德島縣等地，經常用於和式甜點的製作。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.01,0:20:58.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想回去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.05,0:21:03.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  好想家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.91,0:21:07.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是這些真的賣得出去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.27,0:21:09.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然擺得很整齊的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.93,0:21:12.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  這個一個多少錢？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.17,0:21:14.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客人來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.21,0:21:15.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.50,0:21:17.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說到底是多少錢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.46,0:21:19.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  大福一個多少…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.16,0:21:21.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和三盆的不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.30,0:21:26.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不幹呢  我才不用草莓什麼的來做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.47,0:21:30.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.10,0:21:32.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,免費贈送
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.66,0:21:33.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  LUCKY
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
